					<![CDATA[
						 <p>That won't quite work though, which was the point of the last experiment. Cheesed anomalies are still anomalous, in new and interesting and unpredictable ways. So cheesing everything is probably not a very good idea, least you end up with cheese clusters spontaneously growing under your skin whenever you think of color purple. Plus there's the issue of the limited availability of 1600-1.</p> 
