					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-466570#post-1452276</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-466570/scp-1600#post-1452276</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 18 May 2012 05:30:09 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>anqxyr</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>966960</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>In this case the researches had an excuse: during numerous tests on normal materials the resulting samples always turned out to be safe and edible, no matter what kind of materials were used - acids, explosives, radioactive ores, anything. So, at least one test was required to see if 1600-1 can neutralize anomalous materials. And while the result was once again safe and even sort of helpful, it still had some anomalous properties, so any further in-universe cross-tests would probably require a very good reason and a lot more paperwork.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
