				<wikidot:authorName>anqxyr</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>966960</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Honestly, I don't want it becoming too bloated with test logs. There is a big potential for cross testing here, and if everyone would start adding more stuff the result could be detrimental.</p> <p>You know what? Could maybe people who want to add tests with their SCP objects, or other's SCP objects with permission, or even interesting non anomalous items PM their idea to me through wikidot, using current material/appearance/notes format? If there will be at least 10 tests, I'll create a supplement page for them and link it from the main article. If after a week or so there would be only few suggestions, I'll add them directly to the article.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
